main event: A UFO sighting was reported on April 3, 1961, in Hialeah, Florida, where an object in the sky came out of nowhere and disappeared.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at 2215Z and lasted for 1 minute., The object was considered as possibly being an aircraft., The object was described as coming out of nowhere and then disappearing., The sighting involved only one object., The report included a request for further UFO information from the Air Force.
witness description: The witness thought the object might have been an aircraft.
